N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4627.16 - Recording determination of appeal

State Regulations

Upon the determination of an appeal, the commission shall
state the commission's findings and record the vote of the members
participating therein. All parties shall be notified by the commission of its
determination and shall be furnished a copy of the findings. Notes
